data.value: SELECT 1 AS `C1`, `UnionAll1`.`Id` AS `C2`, `UnionAll1`.`Name` AS `C3`, `UnionAll1`.`MinAge` AS `C4`, `UnionAll1`.`SupplierId` AS `C5` FROM ((SELECT `Extent1`.`Id`, `Extent1`.`Name`, `Extent1`.`MinAge`, `Extent1`.`SupplierId` FROM `Toys` AS `Extent1`) UNION ALL (SELECT `Id`, `Name`, `MinAge`, `SupplierId` FROM `Toys` LIMIT 0)) AS `UnionAll1`
